Appellants (hereafter plaintiffs), purporting to act on behalf of a class consisting of all Pennsylvania residents 
}
{\f2 \b1 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_708_768_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_708_768_1}
